{"tid":1061547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲國中生帶小女友私奔！去完賓館被逮才知她28歲","createTime":"2019-03-14T12:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T15:02:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"202b7e282ca3b65687872756b098fda7b9b1b395","tid":1061547,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"日本一名14歲國三少年日前在網上結識13歲少女，雙方相談甚歡，還到賓館發生關係。今年1月，少年決定與女生私奔，留下一張紙條後就離家出走。不過警方找到2人時，發現女方其實已經28歲，而且是一位粉領上班族，讓少年非常錯愕。<br />\n <br />\n根據《神戶新聞》報導，這名28歲OL去年8月在網路聊天室結識14歲少年，還跟對方到神戶市賓館發生關係。<br />\n <br />\n起初少年雙親並不知情，是直到少年今年1月突然離家出走，還留下一張「我想跟她在一起」的紙條，這段戀情才曝光。<br />\n <br />\n兵庫縣警方偵辦後，本月12日循線找到2人，依違反縣青少年愛護條例逮捕女子，但少年供稱「她跟我說她比我小1歲」；目前已確認女子是大分市某公司職員，現年28歲，全案調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QLZ2w1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QLZ2w1.png&h=2cff6c6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1fa689a664d624ba1eea27a955dc32e59731a7b","tid":1061547,"uid":46245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"正面圖呢？"},{"pid":"18216273fab0d5f100db1274f9310aa84a094d0b","tid":1061547,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1fa689a664d624ba1eea27a955dc32e59731a7b","tid":1061547,"uid":46245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"正面圖呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"想喺荒島食山珍海味? 會唔會貪心過頭?"},{"pid":"462821783614fa057da893d585553f41c905ccc3","tid":1061547,"uid":128603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qYEifF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qYEifF.jpg&h=0edfb978&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c28b6ed95d2294e1e8372ac97066a37b1b5ae02","tid":1061547,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"一定細細粒童顏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{